overview: Featured special Anniversary Edition of AEW Dynamite including a title match for the AEW World Championship: Lance Archer vs. Jon Moxley, the AEW World Tag Team titles: FTR vs. Best Friends, the TNT Championship: Orange Cassidy vs. Cody, and the AEW Women's World Championship: Big Swole vs. Hikaru Shida.
title: AEW Dynamite Anniversary Show
